{"tid":1005782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪洗慣朋友錢會有依賴性？","createTime":"2019-02-02T12:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T16:12:33.000Z","uid":212721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"028f788adae6a8b47e7cfcc3ffcf6576ffeede68","tid":1005782,"uid":212721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"讀緊書<br />\n屋企算係有少少錢<br />\n兩老收入加埋十幾萬<br />\n冇返工，屋企人比錢我洗<br />\n平均一個月有8000蚊可以用。<br />\n<br />\n身邊啲fd普通家庭<br />\n初初同朋友出去食野消費，<br />\n佢地冇錢或唔夠錢我會幫佢地比住先。<br />\n因為我比較鍾意食野，有時佢地冇錢出去<br />\n我會直情請佢地食，當比錢佢地陪我食飯。<br />\n但最近發現有一兩個成日想搵我賣單<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中有個fd屋企算窮，出街不時搵我借錢比佢用<br />\n初初係冇乜所謂，但後尾窮到連幾蚊都要問我借<br />\n想買野食都直接叫我比錢，同我講佢想食叫我比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n本身真係唔介意，但慢慢就好似當我財務公司咁<br />\n一冇錢第一時間諗起問我借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又同佢好fd，唔識拒絕<br />\n前幾排，我終於頂唔順開口拒絕，之後佢就閪哂面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撇除呢啲樣佢地其實都幾好人，自己都鍾意同佢地出街<br />\n我唔想冇左佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係咪我嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8061775db6fbe28f86f38db2997aaadb6ec31889","tid":1005782,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"扮無錢囉可以點"},{"pid":"6517b38c92d3a93401baebe1559f5fdf71073af8","tid":1005782,"uid":212721,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8061775db6fbe28f86f38db2997aaadb6ec31889","tid":1005782,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"扮無錢囉可以點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:51:03.000Z","msg":"點扮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl